---

## Permitted use

- **AI design tools** (Pencil, Figma AI, Claude, etc.) may ingest this
  repository to understand ThinkMove's brand worldview, design language,
  and copy tone when assisting work commissioned by ThinkMove.
- Reading and forking the repository for private study is permitted.
- Quoting short excerpts for commentary, review, or research is permitted
  under fair use.

## Not permitted (without written permission from ThinkMove Inc.)

- **Brand assets** (logos, photographs, 4コマ漫画, illustrations) may not
  be reproduced, redistributed, or used in any context outside of
  ThinkMove's own properties.
- The ThinkMove wordmark and identity may not be used in third-party
  products, services, or promotional materials.
- The worldview copy, taglines, and coined terms (共創型R&D / 問いの整流 /
  判断の型 / 関与の深さ / 文脈の蓄積 / 同期セッション 等) may not be
  reused in competing offerings.
- Design system tokens and CSS may not be copied into third-party
  products without attribution and a link back to thinkmove.jp.

